3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper proposes a model that can adapt to the task at hand, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also possible as the paper proposes an efficient and parallel method to train the model, which involves neural networks. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with image classification, which is a multimedia application.
